DGATE.IS.long_name: Datagate Bilgisayar Malzemeleri Ticaret Anonim Sriketi
DGATE.IS.summary: Datagate Bilgisayar Malzemeleri Ticaret Anonim Sirketi distributes information technology products in Turkey. It offers smart phones, tablets, modems, notebooks, and accessories, as well as security, wearable technology, smart living, and computer products. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Istanbul, Turkey.
